Class LinkedBag<T>

java.lang.Object
LinkedBag<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
BagInterface<T>
public class LinkedBag<T> extends Object implements BagInterface<T>
The class LinkedBag implements the ADT bag using a linked list.
